{
  "stem": "1183.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had to walk through the snow-- and in the winter, was it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We left Auschwitz in [INAUDIBLE] August.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in June-- six week, July, August, we left Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we walked all the way to the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The factory was work and a huge factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, more or less, in kind of a glass cage, more or less the same work as what I did in Holland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I couldn't work too well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had 12-hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had barely enough to eat, barely enough sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our sleep was interrupted by the bombings what the Air Force did, the English Air Force.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they didn't produce.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And many time that I just remember falling asleep, and then one of those supervisors came, and oh, [INAUDIBLE], You're up again and you woke up again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- there was there, naturally, a washroom, and it was the communication room where we get the latest news, what is the war, when it's finished, and how-- and where are the Russians and, you know, what's happening.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were timed when we went past the desk-- son of a gun, one of the supervisors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we were timed that we're not too long, because naturally, they knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was also one woman there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was herself and-- not from the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She lived there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she was also maybe forced to work there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She was very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She called me by-- I'd say Miss Mossel, you know, you have no name, nothing, so Fraulein or Miss Mossel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She had respect and she felt for us, but there's not much she can do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some other women I know got something, but they were older.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They knew how to work the ropes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
